OL,3,CTransport Minister to set out how
OL,4,C20mph zones across Wales will change
OL,6,FThe Transport Secretary will set out
OL,7,Flater today (Tuesday) how changes to
OL,8,F20mph zones will be made in the coming
OL,9,Fmonths.
OL,11,Fis expected to announce that there
OL,12,Fwill be new guidance and money to help
OL,13,Flocal councils change some roads back
OL,14,Fto 30mph, with 20mph limits targeted
OL,15,Fon areas around schools, hospitals,
OL,16,Fwhere elderly people are at risk, and
OL,17,Fin built-up areas.
