OL,3,CTransport Minister to set out how
OL,4,C20mph zones across Wales will change
OL,6,FSince September 2023, local
OL,7,Fauthorities here in Wales have been
OL,8,Fobliged to set speed limits in urban
OL,9,Fand residential areas at 20mph as a
OL,10,Fdefault, even though they can keep
OL,11,Fsome of those roads at 30mph.
OL,13,FMr Skates will set out the changes in
OL,14,Fa statement to Senedd members this
OL,15,Fafternoon updating them on the Welsh
OL,16,FGovernment's transport priorities. The
OL,17,Fbulk of the statement is expected to
OL,18,Fbe devoted to the 20mph policy.
