OL,3,CTransport Minister to set out how
OL,4,C20mph zones across Wales will change
OL,6,FThat policy has been hugely
OL,7,Fcontroversial since it came into force
OL,8,Fsix months ago. A petition to the
OL,9,FSenedd gathered nearly 470,000
OL,10,Fsignatures, the .
OL,12,FA change of leadership has brought a
OL,13,Fchange of tone. During his leadership
OL,14,Fcampaign, said that there would be a
OL,15,Freview of the way that the policy has
OL,16,Fbeen implemented.
