OL,3,CTransport Minister to set out how
OL,4,C20mph zones across Wales will change
OL,6,FKen Skates has continued that new
OL,7,Fapproach since becoming Transport
OL,8,FSecretary. He told Senedd Members last
OL,9,Fweek that, "I desperately want to help
OL,10,Fto change the tone and tenor of the
OL,11,Fdebate on transport."
OL,13,FHe's expected to announce that
OL,14,Fthere'll be new guidance for local
OL,15,Fauthorities to help them make more
OL,16,Froads exempt from the 20mph default
OL,17,Fpolicy.
