OL,3,CTransport Minister to set out how
OL,4,C20mph zones across Wales will change
OL,6,FThe number of roads likely to change
OL,7,Fback to 30mph could vary considerably
OL,8,Facross Wales. Last week, the leaders
OL,9,Fof Cardiff and Swansea councils said
OL,10,Fthat they expected around half a dozen
OL,11,Froads to be affected. Officials
OL,12,Festimate that in other authorities the
OL,13,Fnumber could be much higher.
OL,15,FMr Skates has already said that the
OL,16,FWelsh Government will cover the costs
OL,17,Fof any new changes. The original cost
OL,18,Fof implementing the policy was #30m.
OL,19,FThese new changes are expected to cost
OL,20,Fmuch less.
