OL,4,C20mph zones across Wales will change
OL,6,FThe change in tone has already been
OL,7,Fwelcomed by those within the Labour
OL,8,Fgroup who've expressed concerns.
OL,10,FThe MS for Caerphilly, Hefin David,
OL,11,F"Several of us in the Labour Senedd
OL,12,FGroup, while supportive of the
OL,13,Fprinciple of extended 20mph zones, had
OL,14,Fconcerns about this approach to its
OL,15,Fintroduction."
