OL,3,CTransport Minister to set out how
OL,4,C20mph zones across Wales will change
OL,6,FHe went on to say: "The policy of
OL,7,Fintroducing 20mph where people and
OL,8,Fvehicles mix is an excellent one. The
OL,9,Fchanges proposed by Ken Skates will
OL,10,Fmake sure that exactly such a policy
OL,11,Fis in place in Wales."
OL,13,FPolitical opponents are less welcoming.
OL,15,FWelsh Conservative Leader Andrew RT
OL,16,FDavies said: "Any change to the
OL,17,Fguidance will be cosmetic, and
OL,18,Fcosmetic changes will not fool the
OL,19,FWelsh public.
