OL,3,CTransport Minister to set out how
OL,4,C20mph zones across Wales will change
OL,6,F"Smoke and mirrors around guidance
OL,7,Fwill not do. This policy needs to be
OL,8,Fscrapped in its entirety."
OL,10,FPlaid Cymru leader Rhun ap Iorwerth
OL,11,Fsaid: "I support the principle of
OL,12,Fwidespread 20mph zones, but it's clear
OL,13,Fthat it was implemented very poorly
OL,14,Fand inconsistently, with too many
OL,15,Froads changing to 20mph in places
OL,16,Fwhere it felt unreasonable.
