OL,3,CTransport Minister to set out how
OL,4,C20mph zones across Wales will change
OL,6,F"Welsh Government must push ahead now
OL,7,Fand sort it out, working with local
OL,8,Fauthorities and communities to ensure
OL,9,Fthat limits are properly reviewed, and
OL,10,Funreasonable 20mphs are removed."
OL,12,FMeanwhile the Wales Green Party leader
OL,13,FAnthony Slaughter said: "It's beyond
OL,14,Fdisappointing that this backward step
OL,15,Fis even being considered. The 20mph
OL,16,Flimit works and makes our streets
OL,17,Fsafer and more welcoming for all
OL,18,Fusers. The data proves this."
